<plot>Inspired by the Chaplin silent film era of the 1920s, this twelve-minute short follows the adventures of Chastine as she roller skates into a perilous world filled with thugs and strangers. Alone and forced to rely solely on her wits, Chastine thwarts a gang of thugs, using a broken pair of roller skates to retrieve her beloved bottle of Chanel perfume.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100861</url></doc>
